[
{ type: install
  message: <<EOM

Thank you for installing Iocaine, the deadliest poison known to AI.

To enable iocaine, set 'iocaine_enable="YES"' in rc.conf

Configuration files are located at %%ETCDIR%%/iocaine/
For configuration details please check the official documentation at
https://iocaine.madhouse-project.org/configuration/


Iocaine should run behind a web server acting as a reverse-proxy. For
this iocaine by default listens on localhost (127.0.0.1) port 42069.

An example configuration for nginx can be found at
https://iocaine.madhouse-project.org/documentation/3/reverse-proxies/nginx/
EOM
}
]
